Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Setup", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.798796435942964*^9, 
  3.798796436623301*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7e2a2be1-0542-40c3-85e1-\
29e9dbcb99d2"],

Cell["\<\
The transition matrix used describes the dwell times of a myosin motor at a \
given position on actin given. Reaches a single absorbing state when the \
motor either take a forward/backward step or detaches completely from actin. 

The columns represent the following states:
1) Resting state. 
2) Trailing head detached, pre ATP hydrolysis. 
3) Post ATP hydrolysis. 
4) Free head attaches to forward position, pre power-stroke. 
5) Free head binds to original position on actin, pre power-stroke.
6) Leading head detached.
7) Detached state.

The rates used are as follows:
kd1: rate of trailing head detachment from resting state. Encapsulates the \
rates of ADP release and ATP binding to head required for detachment.
kd2: rate of leading head detachment from resting state. Not ADP nor ATP \
dependent.
kh: rate of ATP hydrolysis
kfpp: The inverse first mean passage time of a diffusing myosin head to find \
the forward binding position on actin.
kfpm: The inverse first mean passage time of a diffusing myosin head to find \
the reverse binding position on actin.
kps: The rate of the power-stroke.
b: Binding penalty for needing to re-bend a myosin neck during certain \
rebinding events. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.801388270373262*^9, 3.801388390694542*^9}, {
  3.8013884250337343`*^9, 3.8013888675945883`*^9}, {3.801389225518199*^9, 
  3.801389227792776*^9}, {3.856076879688238*^9, 
  3.85607689125214*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b888c9e1-204b-477c-9ad9-\
6a448b003db7"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"(*", " ", 
   RowBox[{"The", " ", "transition", " ", "matrix", " ", "described", " ", 
    RowBox[{"above", "."}]}], " ", "*)"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"omega", "=", 
     RowBox[{"(", "\[NoBreak]", GridBox[{
        {
         RowBox[{"-", 
          RowBox[{"(", 
           RowBox[{"kd1", "+", "kd2"}], ")"}]}], "0", "0", "0", "kps", 
         RowBox[{"b", " ", "kfpp"}], "0"},
        {"kd1", 
         RowBox[{"-", 
          RowBox[{"(", 
           RowBox[{"kd1", "+", "kh"}], ")"}]}], "0", "0", "0", "0", "0"},
        {"0", "kh", 
         RowBox[{"-", 
          RowBox[{"(", 
           RowBox[{"kfpp", "+", 
            RowBox[{"b", " ", "kfpm"}], "+", "kd1"}], ")"}]}], "0", "0", "0", 
         "0"},
        {"0", "0", "kfpp", 
         RowBox[{"-", "kps"}], "0", "0", "0"},
        {"0", "0", 
         RowBox[{"b", " ", "kfpm"}], "0", 
         RowBox[{"-", "kps"}], "0", "0"},
        {"kd2", "0", "0", "0", "0", 
         RowBox[{"-", 
          RowBox[{"(", 
           RowBox[{"kfpm", "+", 
            RowBox[{"b", " ", "kfpp"}], "+", "kd1"}], ")"}]}], "0"},
        {"0", "kd1", "kd1", "kps", "0", 
         RowBox[{"kd1", "+", "kfpm"}], "0"}
       }], "\[NoBreak]", ")"}]}], ";"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
   RowBox[{"omega", "//", "MatrixForm"}]}]}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.798794540691429*^9, 3.798794556866293*^9}, {
  3.7987952701796913`*^9, 3.7987952840844316`*^9}, {3.798795318707299*^9, 
