Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Run velocity expressions", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.801390155799439*^9, 3.801390168986044*^9}, {
  3.801390499276568*^9, 
  3.801390501174321*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"ae79a6e6-1766-4033-af7c-\
8eb153fd00f9"],

Cell["\<\
The following derives expressions pertaining to a motor\[CloseCurlyQuote]s \
run velocity. 

The following notation is used.
pF: Probability of a forward step conditioned on probability of the motor not \
stomping.
pB: Probability of a backwards step conditioned on probability of the motor \
not stomping.
pT: Probability of the motor terminating conditioned on probability of the \
motor not stomping.
i: Number of forward steps during a trajectory.
j: Number of backward steps during a trajectory.
\[Alpha]: Approximating shape parameter of dwell times.
\[Theta]: Approximating scale parameter of dwell times.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.80140097137004*^9, 3.8014010194062347`*^9}, {
  3.801401108498126*^9, 3.801401192644416*^9}, {3.8014012753350773`*^9, 
  3.8014013086898193`*^9}, {3.801401729700135*^9, 3.801401761179193*^9}, {
  3.801405264740279*^9, 3.801405329328706*^9}, {3.8014053985207233`*^9, 
  3.801405719015511*^9}, {3.801405759447215*^9, 3.801405812283922*^9}, {
  3.8014058661725893`*^9, 
  3.801405941586994*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b541d261-e84d-4652-a7d3-\
cd86b72c41c4"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["The general run velocity density", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.801390321226367*^9, 3.801390323002705*^9}, {
  3.801406038204152*^9, 
  3.801406053867282*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7015621a-9529-470c-becf-\
c2a699bd7143"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "In general, the run velocity density is of the form ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox["f", "vrun"], "(", "v", ")"}], "="}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->"TraditionalForm",ExpressionUUID->
  "f8953f69-7d94-42c0-99ca-7e277b03f5d7"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    UnderoverscriptBox["\[Sum]", 
     RowBox[{"z", "=", "0"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
    RowBox[{
     SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", "0", "\[Infinity]"], 
     RowBox[{"f", 
      RowBox[{"(", 
       RowBox[{"z", ",", "t"}], ")"}], "\[Delta]", 
      RowBox[{"(", 
       RowBox[{"v", "-", 
        FractionBox["z", "t"]}], ")"}], 
      RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "t"}]}]}]}], ",", " ", 
   RowBox[{"z", "\[NotEqual]", " ", "0"}]}]],ExpressionUUID->
  "d86424aa-71c3-4a00-a3de-1d656bd475d0"],
 ". The case when z=0 is a delta contribution equal the probability of a zero \
run distance."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8014059470847816`*^9, 3.801405978344101*^9}, {
  3.801412038091456*^9, 3.801412078290443*^9}, {3.801412112543312*^9, 
  3.8014122175042887`*^9}, {3.801421975488023*^9, 
